  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-01 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Higher model risk drives stricter credibility requirements; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Full 13-factor assessment covering verification, validation, and uncertainty quantification activities. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: This package is a synthetic adversarial sample targeting W-AR-01 — one credibility factor carries a requiredLevel with no structured acceptanceCriteria field.",
  "assuranceLevel": "Low",
